## Overview
Extends NATS client with JetStream support for durable streams, consumers, and
exactly-once delivery semantics.

## Background
JetStream is NATS' persistence layer providing:
- Durable message streams
- Pull and push consumers
- Exactly-once delivery with ack/nack
- Stream replication for HA

## Design

### Stream Management
```rust
