### Cancel-Correct Consumption
```rust
// Messages are obligations until acked or nacked
impl JsMessage {
    fn drop(&mut self) {
        if !self.ack_handle.is_committed() {
            // Log warning: message not explicitly acked/nacked
            // JetStream will redeliver after ack_wait
        }
    }
}
```

